Growing old is an inevitable process and aging graciously requires a healthy 
body where oral cavity occupies an important place. Geriatric dentistry is a 
specialized multidisciplinary branch of general dentistry designed to provide 
dental services to elderly patients. The rise in life expectancy has attributed 
to the substantial reduction in mortality which brought about by improved health 
care facilities, sanitation, environmental and public health reforms coupled 
